# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Frontend (Vite) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`) and fill in your values.
# All `VITE_*` vars are exposed to the browser bundle вЂ” never put secrets here.

# Supabase project вЂ” required for auth, data, storage, realtime.
# Get these from your Supabase project dashboard в†’ Settings в†’ API.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project-ref.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-public-key

# Optional: GitHub Pages base path override (defaults to repo name in CI).
# VITE_BASE_PATH=/project-requirements-portal/

# в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ ITHub integration (read by the Edge Function, NOT exposed to browser) в”Ђв”Ђ
# When VITE_ITHUB_MOCK=true, the Edge Function returns hardcoded mock tickets
# instead of calling ITHub. Use this for local dev without ITHub credentials.
VITE_ITHUB_MOCK=true

# Optional: base URL of the ITHub portal used for deep-link "ењЁ ITHub дё­ж‰“ејЂ" buttons.
VITE_ITHUB_PORTAL_BASE=https://demo.logicalisservice.com